node.title: Blackcaps' tour to Australia officially postponed
node.description: The Blackcaps had been scheduled to play three one-day internationals and a Twenty20 international, starting January 30.
node.content: ["The Blackcaps' upcoming tour to Australia has been officially postponed.", "On Wednesday, NZ Cricket announced current MIQ demands and the ongoing uncertainty surrounding the border situation had made the tour unfeasible.", "The Blackcaps were scheduled to take on the Australians in a three-match one-day international series and one-off Twenty20 international.", "The squad was due to leave on Monday, with the first ODI to be played at Perth on January 30.", "NZ Cricket says it remains hopeful for the return three-match T20 home series to proceed as planned in March.", "More to come", "\u00a0"]
